quran[6{c,v,t}:
9,21,un ka rab inhen apni rehmat aur khushnodi aur aisijannaton ki basharat deta hai jahan un ke liye paidaar aish ke samaan hain
9,22,un mein woh hamesha rahen ge yaqeenan Allah ke paas khidmaat ka sila dainay ko bohat kuch hai
9,23,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apne bapon aur bhaiyon ko bhi apna Rafeeq nah banaao agar woh imaan par kufar ko tarjeeh den tum mein se jo un ko Rafeeq banayen ge wohi zalim hon ge"
9,24,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, keh do ke agar tumahray baap aur tumahray betay, aur tumahray bhai, aur tumhari biwiyan aur tumahray Aziz o Iqareb aur tumahray woh maal jo tum ne kama ye hain, aur tumahray woh kaarobar jin ke maand par jaane ka tum ko khauf hai aur tumahray woh ghar jo tum ko pasand hain, tum ko Allah aur is ke rasool aur is ki raah mein jehaad se Aziz tar hain to intzaar karo yahan taq ke Allah apna faisla tumahray samnay le aeye, aur Allah fasik logon ki rahnumai nahi kya karta"
9,25,Allah is se pehlay bohat se mawaqay par tumhari madad kar chuka hai abhi Ghazwah Hunain ke roz ( uss ki dastgeeri ki shaan tum dekh chuke ho ) is roz tumhe apni kasrat tadaad ka Ghara tha magar woh tumahray kuch kaam nah aayi aur zameen apni wusat ke bawajood tum par tang ho gayi aur tum peeth phair kar bhaag niklay
9,26,phir Allah ne apni sakinat (calm) apne rasool par aur momnin par nazil farmai aur woh lashkar utaarey jo tum ko nazar nah atay thay aur munkareen haq ko saza di ke yahi badla hai unn logon ke liye jo haq ka inkaar karen
